    "description": {
        "en-US": "This add-on integrates Thunderbird with the Windows Aero interface. Note that the glass effect is available only on <b>Windows Vista</b> and <b>Windows 7</b>.\n\nUnofficial x64 builds of Thunderbird are NOT supported. However, you can still use this add-on with a standard 32-bit version of Thunderbird on a 64-bit operating system.\n\nThis add-on does NOT work with Thunderbird 2.0.0.*. Please upgrade your Thunderbird to the latest version.\n\n\n<b>Enhanced Glasser Theme</b>\nGlasser for Thunderbird includes a new, improved theme for Thunderbird to provide a better integration with the Windows 7 interface. If you use your own theme, you may want to disable this feature:\n1. Open Tools -&gt; Options...\n2. On the Advanced page, select the General tab\n3. Click the Config Editor button. Clear any warning message that is displayed\n4. Enter 'glasser' (no quotes) in the search box\n5. Double-click on the preference called \"extensions.glasser.enableTheme\"\n6. Restart Thunderbird\n\n\n\n<i>Glasser for Thunderbird is based on Glasser for Firefox, developed by <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://outgoing.prod.mozaws.net/v1/5db4b40c82a882869ee9619ce9cb2bb91655bda9ef44b01904694b0742e22413/http%3A//www.sixxgate.com/\">6XGate</a>.</i>"
    },
